WEBVTT

00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:32.336
Nemamo 70 i više godina da to riješimo,

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:34.896
znači moramo pokušati nešto novo

00:14:34.920 --> 00:14:37.080
i nešto drugačije.

00:14:38.400 --> 00:14:40.560
Rješenje kreće s reformama.

00:14:41.880 --> 00:14:45.856
Moramo uvesti reforme i komercijalizirati

00:14:45.880 --> 00:14:48.416
poljoprivredne industrije u Africi

00:14:48.440 --> 00:14:49.640
i Indiji.

00:14:50.320 --> 00:14:52.456
Pod komercijalizacijom

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:55.616
ne mislim samo na komercijalne
poljoprivredne djelatnosti,

00:14:55.640 --> 00:14:58.216
već i na upotrebu podataka

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:00.536
u cilju izrade boljih politika,